---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Security Statement"
  description="Learn about FlowFuse's commitment to security, compliance, and protecting your industrial data."
>
  <div class="w-full py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="i-heroicons-shield-check text-5xl text-indigo-600 mb-6 block mx-auto" />
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">Security Statement</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Security is at the core of everything we do at FlowFuse. We're committed to protecting
          your industrial data with enterprise-grade security measures.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Security Features -->
      <div class="space-y-8 mb-16">
        <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-3">Data Encryption</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            All data is encrypted in transit using TLS 1.2+ and at rest using AES-256.
            Your industrial data is protected at every stage.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-3">Single Sign-On (SSO)</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Integrate with your existing identity provider using SAML 2.0. Centralize user
            management and enforce your organization's authentication policies.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-3">Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Define granular permissions for team members. Control who can view, edit, and
            deploy Node-RED applications across your organization.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-3">Audit Logging</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Complete audit trail of all actions taken within FlowFuse. Track changes,
            deployments, and user activity for compliance and troubleshooting.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-3">Infrastructure Security</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            FlowFuse Cloud runs on secure, SOC 2 compliant infrastructure with regular
            security assessments and vulnerability scanning.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <div class="text-center bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">Questions About Security?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Our team is happy to discuss your security requirements and provide additional details.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact-us/"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-indigo-600 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors"
        >
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
